{"tid":731543,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【身唔係有屎唔care】大陸品牌Vivo　竟爆出手機相機恐怖彈出錄音醜聞","createTime":"2018-07-06T09:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T09:07:03.000Z","uid":168366,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9e777ec13e7900cfd575973092a0208e8e0f43b3","tid":731543,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/07/dapinpaivivokuangzhuxianggangkoljingbaochushouxiangkongbuchuyin/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F07%2Fdapinpaivivokuangzhuxianggangkoljingbaochushouxiangkongbuchuyin%2F&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7Cx5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a898de18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/07/dapinpaivivokuangzhuxianggangkoljingbaochushouxiangkongbuchuyin/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同樣唔太理香港傳媒感受的大陸品牌Vivo，近日花了勁多預算，全部都放在所謂KOL，請他們去俄羅斯世界盃，由KOL不停為其品牌唱好。唯大陸人使用這部手機的時候，也覺得監控得太過離譜，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">瀏覽網站時，相機竟然恐怖地彈出。打字時，鍵盤竟然走去錄音</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/vivo-nex-camera-recording-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fvivo-nex-camera-recording-1.jpg&h=31200088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，大陸品牌Vivo和百度都發出聲明，堅持這是個誤會，百度更公佈了方法如何去暫時解決問題。百度輸入強調，他們不會用任何方法去收集用戶私隱。當然，信不信由大家決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012d2c8799876e78e167037f6052fe42e5b28078","tid":731543,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"照妖鏡<img src=\"/ass